":guilabel:`Max`: maximum allowed download bandwidth, if empty no upper limit"
" will be set"
msgstr ""

#: ../../firewall.rst:467
msgid "Limits under :guilabel:`Upload bandwidth limits` section:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../firewall.rst:469
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Min`:  minimum reserved upload bandwidth, if empty no upload "
"reservation will be created"
msgstr ""

#: ../../firewall.rst:470
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Max`: maximum allowed download bandwidth, if empty no upper limit"
" will be created"
msgstr ""

